text:
error free =
-spacing is uniform
-fonts are reasonable
-no spelling mistakes
-skill listing is comprehensive, organized and easy to skim
-50 word summary covers what you can do and what you want to do
-all links work
-all experience follows bock's rule
-all education is presented clearly, with supporting courses listed
-projects are clearly presented and linked
